OL,3,CPublic toilets under threat in
OL,4,CEastbourne as council tries to save
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FSo the council is consulting on
OL,8,Fproposals to introduce a community
OL,9,Ftoilet scheme instead, where
OL,10,Fbusinesses could offer their loos for
OL,11,Fpublic use or run some of the
OL,12,Fcouncil's current public toilets.
OL,14,FThe council has committed to keeping
OL,15,Fopen one public loo on the seafront -
OL,16,Fat the bandstand. Campaigners say the
OL,17,Ffour other seafront loos could now
OL,18,Fclose.
OL,20,FThe consultation closes at 5pm on
OL,21,FThursday 31 October 2024.
